node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Luxury Collection in Hotel Grande Bretagne, a Luxury Collection Hotel, Athens with @hotelgrandebretagne. May be an image of 1 person, furniture and indoor.

node.text: Since 1874, @hotelgrandebretagne has welcomed travelers to the heart of Athens, playing a part in historic and political moments as well as diplomatic negotiations over the decades. Learn more about the hotel’s storied past as you admire the artistic masterpieces and antiques on display, and take a seat at Alexander’s Bar to enjoy your choice of premium spirits from the hotel's exclusive collection.

location.name: Hotel Grande Bretagne, a Luxury Collection Hotel, Athens

node.text:
Moments to savor in Santorini

From the 400-year-old wine cellar of @vedema_resort to dining on the Caldera cliffs of @mystique_hotel, catamaran cruises, poolside cocktails and more, discover an exceptional epicurean journey in Santorini.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Luxury Collection in Vedema, a Luxury Collection Resort, Santorini with @vedema_resort. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: Dine under sunset skies on the cliffs of Oia at @vedema_resort. Using vegetables and herbs cultivated from the hotel’s organic farm in the village of Megalohori, every dish features fresh, Greek-inspired flavors, highlighting the region’s rich epicurean heritage.

location.name: Vedema, a Luxury Collection Resort, Santorini

user.full_name: ザ・プリンスギャラリー 東京紀尾井町

node.text: Blooming in March and April, the cherry blossoms in Tokyo create pockets of serenity in a city known for its vibrant energy. Explore centuries-old temples, diverse neighborhoods, and an eclectic culinary scene while visiting @princegallerytokyokioicho.

location.name: The Prince Gallery Tokyo Kioicho,  A Luxury Collection Hotel

user.full_name: ザ・プリンスギャラリー 東京紀尾井町

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Luxury Collection in The Prince Gallery Tokyo Kioicho,  A Luxury Collection Hotel with @princegallerytokyokioicho. May be an image of 1 person, sitting and indoor.

node.text: Once the home of Japan’s ruling aristocracy, Kioicho is now a neighborhood full of history and the perfect start to your Tokyo adventure. Explore the Imperial Palace, head to nearby Ginza for shopping, or simply enjoy the view from over 36 stories above the city from your suite at @princegallerytokyokioicho.

location.name: The Prince Gallery Tokyo Kioicho,  A Luxury Collection Hotel

user.full_name: ザ・プリンスギャラリー 東京紀尾井町

node.text: In the heart of Japan’s bustling capital city, @princegallerytokyokioicho is a sophisticated respite. Soak in the views from the pool or spa and finish the day with a cocktail at the Sky Gallery Lounge Levita — featuring floor-to-ceiling windows and sparkling cityscapes.

location.name: The Prince Gallery Tokyo Kioicho,  A Luxury Collection Hotel

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Luxury Collection in The Jaffa Hotel - Tel Aviv with @thejaffahotel. May be an image of indoor.

node.text: Set within a restored 19th-century complex that was once the Jaffa’s French Hospital, @thejaffahotel is an enclave of quiet beauty for travelers. Featuring many of the building’s original features — from the ancient Crusader wall uncovered during excavations to the polygonal domes and mosaic windows of the chapel — the hotel is a grand display of Neo-Renaissance design in Tel Aviv.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Luxury Collection in Hotel Alfonso XIII, a Luxury Collection Hotel, Seville with @hotelalfonsoxiii. May be an image of outdoors, monument and text that says 'HOTEL'.

node.text: Commissioned by the King of Spain to host international dignitaries during the Ibero-American Exposition of 1929, @hotelalfonsoxiii has remained an iconic cultural landmark in the historic quarter of Santa Cruz, Seville. Blending the original Mudéjar style with Andalusian design, the hotel continues to awe guests with its charm.

location.name: Hotel Alfonso XIII, a Luxury Collection Hotel, Seville

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Luxury Collection in Liberty Hotel Boston with @liberty_hotel. May be an image of indoor and brick wall.

node.text: Built in 1851 as the storied Charles Street Jail, @liberty_hotel is a historic landmark full of character. During the hotel’s transformation, architects worked alongside historians and conservationists to ensure the distinctive personality of the building remained — from the circular windows to the 90-foot-high central atrium.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Luxury Collection in Venice, Italy with @thegrittipalace, and @hoteldanieli. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: From the Basilica and the Bridge of Sighs to cicchetti and Spritz, Venice is a city full of history, culture, and charm. While visiting @thegrittipalace and @hoteldanieli allow our Concierge to guide you to the best sights and hidden treasures of Italy’s floating city.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Luxury Collection in Hotel Danieli, a Luxury Collection Hotel, Venice with @hoteldanieli. May be an image of indoor.

node.text: Dating back to the 14th century, @hoteldanieli is considered one of the most famous hotels in the world and a distinguished example of Venetian excellence. Composed of three palaces located along the lagoon, the hotel welcomes guests to learn about its storied history.

location.name: Hotel Danieli, a Luxury Collection Hotel, Venice

Venetian adventures by yacht with @thegrittipalace

In a city built on over 100 small islands, there’s no better way to explore than by yacht. Travel through the lagoons of Venice aboard a Riva speedboat, learning about the history and heritage of the city known as the “Queen of the Adriatic.”
